  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7509017/" class="title-link">这本书其实原本是另一家出版社约的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7509017"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/130251781/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u130251781-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/130251781/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">陶短房</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-06-24"
      class="main-meta">2015-06-24 22:25:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7509017_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  但编辑屡屡换人要求不断改变，对我这个不善交际的作者而言实在有些困惑，好在老搭档王东军老师接手了……前面的朋友说观点在我别的书中也见过，不假，其实历史类著作若非有新的重大发现，观点不会有大的变化，但观察视角的不同和与其它话题的组合，会不断变化出新的看点

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7509017/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7509017_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7509017_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
